    "随后她将精液全数吞下，瘫倒在我身旁的床上。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:185
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice "voices/jamie_026.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_026.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:186
translate chinese jamie13_e3c704a9:

    # gnd "Wow. That felt amazing."
    gnd "哇。那感觉太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:187
translate chinese jamie13_fc026204:

    # pc "You're telling me."
    pc "你还用说。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:188
translate chinese jamie13_22d66f51:

    # pc "Are you going to stay the night?"
    pc "你要留宿吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:190
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice "voices/jamie_027.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_027.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:191
translate chinese jamie13_30ec8f73:

    # gnd "I probably shouldn't. But I don't feel like moving right now."
    gnd "我大概不该留。但我现在懒得动。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:192
translate chinese jamie13_f1a6c37e:

    # pc "You should stay."
    pc "你应该留下来。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:193
translate chinese jamie13_6d9c381a:

    # gnd "Okay. I think I will."
    gnd "好吧。我想我会留的。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:195
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_8:

    # voice "voices/jamie_028.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_028.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:196
translate chinese jamie13_b095ff70:

    # gnd "Like you said. I'm an adult. I can do what I want."
    gnd "就像你说的。我是个成年人。我想做什么就做什么。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:199
translate chinese jamie13_94cd612d:

    # "She moves to look at me, her eyes locked onto mine."
    "她转过头看着我，目光锁定在我身上。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:201
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_022.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:202
translate chinese jamie13_f9831d1e:

    # gnd "I love you, [pcname]."
    gnd "我爱你，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:203
translate chinese jamie13_5e3e613a:

    # pc "I love you too, Jamie."
    pc "我也爱你，杰米。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:204
translate chinese jamie13_59e15393:

    # "We lie there like that, sweat cooling on our skin, until I hear her soft snoring."
    "我们就那样躺着，汗水在皮肤上渐渐冷却，直到我听到她轻微的鼾声。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:207
translate chinese jamie13_ae4b475d:

    # "Then I fall asleep shortly after."
    "随后我也很快睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:215
translate chinese jamie13_f6d0406e:

    # "In the morning, I wake up to her face, sleeping next to me."
    "清晨，我醒来时，她正睡在我身旁。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:216
translate chinese jamie13_fc00fd18:

    # "I softly caress her cheek to wake her up."
    "我轻轻抚摸她的脸颊，想把她唤醒。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:219
translate chinese jamie13_a336655c:

    # pc "Hey beautiful."
    pc "嘿，美人。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:221
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_10:

    # voice "voices/jamie_029a.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_029a.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:222
translate chinese jamie13_c59c4cdd:

    # gnd "Oh geez, what time is it?"
    gnd "哦天哪，现在几点了？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:224
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_11:

    # voice "voices/jamie_029b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_029b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:225
translate chinese jamie13_9a2ed43d:

    # gnd "I have to get home before Dad gets upset."
    gnd "我得在爸爸发火前赶回家。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:227
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_12:

    # voice "voices/jamie_029c.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_029c.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:228
translate chinese jamie13_c042afc8:

    # gnd "I need a shower too. I smell like sex so bad."
    gnd "我得冲个澡。我身上这股做爱味太重了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:231
translate chinese jamie13_dffd2cad:

    # "She jumps up out of bed, seemingly completely awake now, and starts getting dressed."
    "她从床上跳起来，看来已经完全清醒了，开始穿衣服。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:232
translate chinese jamie13_8d3da257:

    # gnd "Seriously though, [pcname], last night was amazing."
    gnd "说真的，[pcname]，昨晚太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:233
translate chinese jamie13_ec35244f:

    # gnd "I wish I could sleep with you every night."
    gnd "真希望每晚都能和你睡在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:234
translate chinese jamie13_ef7afd6d:

    # pc "You could if you wanted."
    pc "你想的话随时都可以。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:235
translate chinese jamie13_bbd8e0f5:

    # gnd "Maybe one day."
    gnd "也许有一天吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:238
translate chinese jamie13_b00d8df6:

    # "I put on my pajamas and walk her down the stairs."
    "我穿上睡衣，陪她走下楼梯。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:239
translate chinese jamie13_9b857853:

    # "The morning light shining on her from the front windows of the house makes her seem like she's glowing."
    "晨光透过房子的前窗照在她身上，让她看起来仿佛在发光。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:242
translate chinese jamie13_5eb86a54:

    # "We stop at the door, kissing goodbye before we open it."
    "我们在门口停下，在开门前吻别。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:243
translate chinese jamie13_9cdd394e:

    # gnd "Bye, [pcname]. We'll talk later."
    gnd "再见，[pcname]。我们待会儿再聊。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:244
translate chinese jamie13_92be29ee:

    # gnd "And hopefully do this again very soon."
    gnd "希望很快就能再这样。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:245
translate chinese jamie13_72475059:

    # pc "I can't wait."
    pc "我等不及了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:249
translate chinese jamie13_7660a175:

    # "Then she turns and opens the door and her father is standing on my front porch."
    "然后她转身开门，她父亲正站在我家门廊上。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:251
translate chinese jamie13_d41d8cd9_13:

    # voice "voices/jamie_030.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_030.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:252
translate chinese jamie13_a60f4c8e:

    # gnd "Oh! Daddy, I just..."
    gnd "“哦！爸爸，我正……”"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:253
translate chinese jamie13_d6386a6a:

    # "Jamie's Dad" "Let's go."
    "Jamie's Dad" "“我们走吧。”"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:254
translate chinese jamie13_64554391:

    # gnd "...okay."
    gnd "“……好的。”"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:257
translate chinese jamie13_c5786232:

    # "They walk away. I can't see Jamie's face, but I can tell she's crying."
    "他们走了。我看不清杰米的脸，但能感觉到她在哭。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:258
translate chinese jamie13_d519e179:

    # "I don't know what to do, so I just let them go."
    "我不知所措，只能任由他们离开。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:259
translate chinese jamie13_0833f49b:

    # "He needs to get over this shit. I know I hurt her in the past, but it was so long ago. And she's an adult now. I just wish she would stand up to him."
    "他该放下这破事了。我知道我过去伤害过她，但那已是久远的事。而且她现在已是成年人。 我只希望她能挺身对抗他。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:260
translate chinese jamie13_fe41f349:

    # "Hopefully, she will talk to him and get this all sorted out."
    "但愿她能和他好好谈谈，把这一切都理顺。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:263
translate chinese jamie13_1dc304ca:

    # "I shut the door and go back inside and get ready for my day."
    "我关上门回到屋里，开始准备新的一天。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:264
translate chinese jamie13_6888669d:

    # "I try to focus on the amazing night and not the bad morning."
    "我试着把注意力放在昨晚的美好时光上，而不是这个糟糕的早晨。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:266
translate chinese jamie13_ab079190:

    # "Later that night..."
    "当晚稍晚些时候……"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:278
translate chinese jamie13b_e331f532:

    # "My phone starts buzzing in my pocket. Jamie's calling. I hope she worked out stuff with her dad."
    "口袋里的手机开始震动。是杰米打来的。希望她已经和她爸爸把事情解决了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:282
translate chinese jamie13b_db1adf95:

    # pc "Hey, baby."
    pc "嘿，宝贝。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:284
translate chinese jamie13b_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_084.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_084.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:285
translate chinese jamie13b_db3d91ac:

    # gnd "I need to tell you something, [pcname]."
    gnd "有件事我得告诉你，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:287
translate chinese jamie13b_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_085.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_085.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:288
translate chinese jamie13b_ec3e201c:

    # gnd "I'm sorry, but our relationship is not going to work out."
    gnd "对不起，但我们的关系没法继续下去了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:289
translate chinese jamie13b_a2a6fb65:

    # pc "What do you mean?"
    pc "什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:291
translate chinese jamie13b_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_086.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_086.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:292
translate chinese jamie13b_cab545aa:

    # gnd "I have to choose between you and my dad. I'm choosing my dad."
    gnd "我必须在你和我爸之间做个选择。我选我爸。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:294
translate chinese jamie13b_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice "voices/jamie_087.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_087.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:295
translate chinese jamie13b_9a5ae475:

    # gnd "I'm sorry. It's over."
    gnd "对不起。结束了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:298
translate chinese jamie13b_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice "voices/jamie_088.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_088.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:299
translate chinese jamie13b_77f7fa61:

    # gnd "Good luck with everything. Please don't try to contact me anymore."
    gnd "祝你一切顺利。请别再联系我了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:300
translate chinese jamie13b_33949145:

    # pc "What? Wait..."
    pc "什么？等等……"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:303
translate chinese jamie13b_bcbbe2f1:

    # "She hung up."
    "她挂断了。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:304
translate chinese jamie13b_439a8efe:

    # "What the fuck? What am I supposed to do now?"
    "搞什么鬼？我现在该怎么办？"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:305
translate chinese jamie13b_a1814c52:

    # "I guess if she doesn't want to be with me, and doesn't want me to talk to her, I have to respect her wishes."
    "我想，既然她不想跟我在一起，也不想跟我说话，我只能尊重她的意愿。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:306
translate chinese jamie13b_f87ec8ec:

    # "But it's bullshit!"
    "但这简直是胡扯！"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:309
translate chinese jamie13b_18c2def7:

    # "I feel like screaming. Like punching something."
    "我真想大喊大叫。真想揍点什么。"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie13.rpy:310
translate chinese jamie13b_32c163d2:

    # "But instead, I lie in bed and seethe in anger until I fall asleep."
    "但我只是躺在床上，怒火中烧，直到睡着。"

